yes">III, 6, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.46" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 46</bibl> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.161" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 161</bibl>. <cit><quote>M. Malvolio,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.144" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 3, 144</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>M. Remorse,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.125" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 2, 125</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 1.3.21" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 3, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>M. La Far,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 3, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an eminent m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 65</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>M. Veroles,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 115</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>Mounseur</emph> and <emph>Mounsieur</emph>).
